settings.name: goal
settings.description: DOC ME

values.name: classic
values.description: Every Item pickup increases fills a progress bar which gives location checks.

values.name: explore
values.description: Each environment will have location checks within each environment. Environments will be locked in the item pool until received.

settings.name: total_locations
settings.description: How many location checks will be added to the playthrough.

settings.name: chests_per_stage
settings.description: The number of chest locations per environment.

settings.name: shrines_per_stage
settings.description: The number of shrine locations per environment.

settings.name: scavengers_per_stage
settings.description: The number of scavenger locations per environment.

settings.name: scanner_per_stage
settings.description: The number of scanners locations per environment.

settings.name: altars_per_stage
settings.description: The number of altars locations per environment.

settings.name: total_revivals
settings.description: How much percent of the items in your pool will be Dio's Best Friends.

settings.name: start_with_revive
settings.description: Start with Dio's Best Friend, for one extra life.

settings.name: final_stage_death
settings.description: Death on the final boss stage counts as a win.

settings.name: begin_with_loop
settings.description: Enable to precollect a full loop of environments.

settings.name: dlc_sotv
settings.description: Enable if you are using Survivors of the Void DLC. Adds Void items to the item pool.

settings.name: item_pickup_step
settings.description: How many item pickups are required before the next one triggers an AP check.

settings.name: shrine_use_step
settings.description: Number of shrines to use up before the next one triggers an AP check.

settings.name: enable_lunar
settings.description: Adds Lunar items to multiworld pool.

settings.name: item_weights
settings.description: The set of weights to be used in this run.

values.name: new
values.description: Proposed preset to replace the current default in the future

values.name: chaos
values.description: Mostly totally random, lower weights for rare stuff

values.name: void
values.description: Every item is a Void item.

settings.name: item_pool_presets
settings.description: Whether to use a preset item pool distribution. If disabled, you'll be able to set item types manually.
